INSERT INTO `breaking_bad` VALUES (1,1,1,'Pilot','/ydlY3iPfeOAvu8gVqrxPoMvzNCn.jpg',NULL,'When an unassuming high school chemistry teacher discovers he has a rare form of lung cancer, he decides to team up with a former student and create a top of the line crystal meth in a used RV, to provide for his family once he is gone.'),(2,1,2,'The Cat\'s in the Bag','/tjDNvbokPLtEnpFyFPyXMOd6Zr1.jpg',NULL,'Walt and Jesse attempt to tie up loose ends. The desperate situation gets more complicated with the flip of a coin. Walt\'s wife, Skyler, becomes suspicious of Walt\'s strange behavior.'),(3,1,3,'...and the Bag\'s in the River','/2kBeBlxGqBOdWlKwzAxiwkfU5on.jpg',NULL,'Walter fights with Jesse over his drug use, causing him to leave Walter alone with their captive, Krazy-8. Meanwhile, Hank has a scared straight moment with Walter Jr. after his aunt discovers he has been smoking pot. Also, Skylar is upset when Walter stays away from home.'),(4,1,4,'Cancer Man','/i5BAJVhuIWfkoSqDID6FnQNCTVc.jpg',NULL,'Walter finally tells his family that he has been stricken with cancer. Meanwhile, the DEA believes Albuquerque has a new, big time player to worry about. Meanwhile, a worthy recipient is the target of a depressed Walter\'s anger, and Jesse makes a surprise visit to his parents home.'),(5,1,5,'Gray Matter','/82G3wZgEvZLKcte6yoZJahUWBtx.jpg',NULL,'Walter and Skyler attend a former colleague\'s party. Jesse tries to free himself from the drugs, while Skyler organizes an intervention.'),(6,1,6,'Crazy Handful of Nothin\'','/hyYwqbmcHn3fuxWE3h4IhZZbkU3.jpg',NULL,'The side effects of chemo begin to plague Walt. Meanwhile, the DEA rounds up suspected dealers.'),(7,1,7,'A No-Rough-Stuff Type Deal','/1dgFAsajUpUT7DLXgAxHb9GyXHH.jpg',NULL,'Walter accepts his new identity as a drug dealer after a PTA meeting. Elsewhere, Jesse decides to put his aunt\'s house on the market and Skyler is the recipient of a baby shower.'),(8,2,1,'Seven Thirty-Seven','/7vVujNqjP23MtPqUTBNITIW3DDA.jpg',NULL,'Walt and Jesse are vividly reminded of Tuco‚Äôs volatile nature, and try to figure a way out of their business partnership. Hank attempts to mend fences between the estranged Marie and Skyler.'),(9,2,2,'Grilled','/vWcFcwMUfeBN8FZEdSSPHGQYrna.jpg',NULL,'Walt and Jesse find themselves in close quarters with an unhinged Tuco. Marie and Hank comfort Skyler, who is distraught over Walt‚Äôs disappearance. Hank pays a visit to Mrs. Pinkman on some not-so-official business.'),(10,2,3,'Bit by a Dead Bee','/p69fPkpnnxUmevhupJiDeYfQxxl.jpg',NULL,'Walt and Jesse become short on cash when they try to cover their tracks. Meanwhile, the DEA has a lead that could them straight to Walt and Jesse.'),(11,2,4,'Down','/9xi18yhtCLrrJ2plZjXgfGqeTjU.jpg',NULL,'Walt attempts to reconnect with his family, while Jesse struggles to rebuild his life.'),(12,2,5,'Breakage','/gkr2GptPkAoDavt71rJd3A4FFZ0.jpg',NULL,'Hank suffers from the aftermath of his encounter with Tuco. Meanwhile, Jesse hires a crew to get their product out on the streets.'),(13,2,6,'Peekaboo','/avu1h4hzWumE9B0nTo14Lfp4E9i.jpg',NULL,'Walt\'s secret is in jeopardy when Skyler thanks Gretchen for paying for his treatment.'),(14,2,7,'Negro Y Azul','/ng5NKNLM3mEUxHKN3Ava1PcZhSs.jpg',NULL,'Jesse and Walt discuss expanding into new territories; Hank struggles to fit in; Skyler pursues a new job opportunity; Jesse gets to know his landlord.'),(15,2,8,'Better Call Saul','/itKNfQ3Nm6Qkjdp0hew5jvqbB8p.jpg',NULL,'Walt and Jesse seek advice from a shady attorney when Badger gets in trouble with the law; the DEA believes they have caught up with \"Heisenberg\" ; Hank returns.'),(16,2,9,'4 Days Out','/j92CoMwArTeQwnGVl12SJaKlI0J.jpg',NULL,'Walt and his family wait for news after he undergoes a PET-CT scan. Walt follows Saul\'s advice; Jesse\'s relationship with Jane is put on hold when he and Walt head to the desert for a marathon of cooking.'),(17,2,10,'Over','/qJvm57aPMMEraJ62bDb79O0XXG9.jpg',NULL,'Walt and Hank get into a heated argument at a party. Skyler opens up to her boss. Jane hides her relationship with Jesse from her father.'),(18,2,11,'Mandala','/yeQAQsV4WPTmKWTyuDhF3DAna1x.jpg',NULL,'When unforeseen circumstances cause Walt and Jesse to lose some dealers, Saul suggests they add a new business partner. At work, Skylar confronts Ted about the unnerving information she had uncovered. Jane learns what Jesse does for a living when he opens up to her, which ends in disastrous results.'),(19,2,12,'Phoenix','/m2fzm9JKgaLPL2U01xROTpBXE4m.jpg',NULL,'As Walt explores money laundering options, he and Jesse spar over the profits from their latest deal. Jesse and Jane clash with her father. Walt makes a fatal decision.'),(20,2,13,'ABQ','/xdSWJjptnLAvFnh5Is6iJPlH1ds.jpg',NULL,'Skylar confronts Walt about his secrecy; Jesse falls apart; and Jane\'s grief-stricken father takes action that results in further tragedy.'),(21,3,1,'No Mas','/gOevWiZjFEeZgJBCQnWySzd6no9.jpg',NULL,'Walt faces a new threat on a new front and deals with an increasingly angry Skyler, who must consider what to do next with her life and the kids\'. Meanwhile, Jesse comes face-to-face with some startling self-revelations.'),(22,3,2,'Caballo Sin Nombre','/h3k5PoJ0RuKBH7OLnT8IbcFWz80.jpg',NULL,'Despite ever-increasing tension between Walt and Skyler, he pulls out all the stops in an effort to reconcile with the family. Elsewhere, Saul is instrumental in getting Jesse involved in a most-unusual investment opportunity.'),(23,3,3,'I.F.T.','/jH2nkMFxuX5tXc832jyDNU4AjKq.jpg',NULL,'Walt ignores Skyler\'s demands, furthering the rift between them and pushing her to break bad. Still suffering from panic and anxiety attacks, Hank crosses a line at work.'),(24,3,4,'Green Light','/1Se5PpvIgUey9MgXmrKkgO8HVye.jpg',NULL,'Walt loses control as he reacts to Skyler\'s news, endangering his job and relationships with Saul and Jesse. Hank throws himself into his blue meth investigation. Jesse enacts a new plan.'),(25,3,5,'Mas','/m2cipfAKEdLR4MIZKA3EiOcTYiZ.j