Jesse\'s safety.'),(34,4,1,'Box Cutter','/2g6dLvOrLE7tpJatonCchLDkDyF.jpg',NULL,'Walt and Jesse face the deadly consequences of their actions. Skyler deals with a puzzling disappearance, as Marie struggles to help Hank with his recovery.'),(35,4,2,'Thirty-Eight Snub','/ozWpAgU14sMmjliqPtBG5gN0yJd.jpg',NULL,'Walt attempts to form a new alliance as he plans his next move. Skyler pushes Walt towards a business opportunity, in hopes of protecting the family.'),(36,4,3,'Open House','/Ac0wu93r4LaZk07wa7PiWpNOOru.jpg',NULL,'Events spiral out of control at Jesse‚Äôs place. Skyler reluctantly asks for Saul‚Äôs help. Marie returns to an old pastime and a friend asks Hank for help.'),(37,4,4,'Bullet Points','/1yxpr4hff0HpblG9ZW5DQQbImQ2.jpg',NULL,'The Cartel takes steps to gain the upper hand. Walt and Skyler share an embarrassing secret with the rest of the family. Jesse‚Äôs activities draw unwanted attention.'),(38,4,5,'Shotgun','/fG0B2tcRYR60JzmKaPUGl8RYDrq.jpg',NULL,'When Jesse goes missing, Walt fears the worst. Skyler has an unlikely reunion. Hank shares some bad news with Detective Tim Roberts.'),(39,4,6,'Cornered','/9noIu7JCbpfNrENPD3G2qeylllC.jpg',NULL,'Skyler makes an unsettling discovery. Walter, Jr. pushes his dad into a questionable purchase. Jesse offers Mike some unexpected help.'),(40,4,7,'Problem Dog','/duDEbjD1ZCs1eH74QkzJhSSwNLk.jpg',NULL,'A frustrated Walt gambles on a risky new plan.  Skyler\'s business venture hits a snag.  Hank recruits Walter, Jr. for an unusual outing.'),(41,4,8,'Hermanos','/kWtsoaPAdfPXEfqufwA44tr9bp6.jpg',NULL,'Skyler develops an unusual solution to her money troubles. Hank enlists Walt to investigate a theory. Walt‚Äôs impatience with Jesse grows.'),(42,4,9,'Bug','/bIU8FJxe1yXvMm7yREwj138Z6x8.jpg',NULL,'Skyler\'s past mistakes come back to haunt her. Gus takes action to thwart his rivals. Jesse seeks Walt\'s help, with mixed results.'),(43,4,10,'Salud','/j2B7GOepMIHz8ayuwm1xAULjlyw.jpg',NULL,'Walt\'s family worries when he doesn\'t 